{"tid":483662,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇公司個工時或假期真係閪成咁","createTime":"2017-11-29T10:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T14:39:05.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e04047cb3529a2cfe14115ec82ddfea3db461f4","tid":483662,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"例如：<br />\nA公司係六天工作但要同事返足七日工，而第六日公司又拆做兩日返，即係星期六返上半日，星期日就返下半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB公司行奴隸假，但實際放公眾假，不過嗰五日非奴隸假嘅公眾假要扣大假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過法律上兩間公司係完全合法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc45d39700c5c9d031bb0adcb49f0dd97d9165e5","tid":483662,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ff1d9773da2b615fc59d18a18e21b15584075b","tid":483662,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"做嗰啲都正傻鳩"},{"pid":"e996351f45c8cb784f0103a3125ca43fefdd68c1","tid":483662,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6816062582e41478c974d338c9c9772e9a0fe2f0","tid":483662,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"assistant grade 7日AL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽到都嚇親 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}